⁦‪@teslascope‬⁩
 
PSA:
We have confirmed that Tesla pulled all iterations of the holiday update
including 2023.44.30.1 through 2023.44.30.4. 
Vehicles that have received these updates will receive a new update within the
next week and includes many bug fixes for issues reported by vehicle
owners. 12/21/23, 5:27 PM
